{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "amandalee", "message": "Hello team, just a quick reminder about our Sales meeting tomorrow at 2pm to discuss our CRM management strategies for Q3. Please come prepared.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "johnsmith", "message": "Thanks for the reminder Amanda. I'll ensure to bring the latest customer feedback reports for discussion.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "product_updates", "user": "maryjones", "message": "Team, we are making excellent progress on the new electric vehicle model. The design phase is almost complete, and we'll be moving into prototyping next week.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "product_updates", "user": "amandalee", "message": "Great job Mary! I'm excited to see the new model. It will certainly be a game-changer in the market.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "johnsmith", "message": "Amanda, I've noticed a significant increase in customer inquiries about our sustainability initiatives. Perhaps we can include this topic in our next team meeting.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "product_updates", "user": "maryjones", "message": "That's a great idea, John. We have been making significant strides in our sustainability efforts, and it would be beneficial to highlight these to our customers.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "amandalee", "message": "Hi team, I was reviewing the sales data from last year and I've noticed that our vehicle performance upgrade packages have had a consistent sales performance. The average prices of these packages were around $7,000. This includes the mileage increase, suspension lifts, and other enhancements.", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales", "channel": "crm_management", "user": "johnsmith", "message": "Thanks for the update, Amanda. That's really helpful. It's good to know that our packages are appreciated by our customers, given their price point. I'll use this data for our upcoming sales strategy planning.", "create_at": 1620500100000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "product_updates", "user": "amandalee", "message": "Hello Product team, just wanted to share an update from the sales side. Last year, our vehicle performance upgrade packages averaged around $7,000. This includes upgrades like mileage increase, suspension lifts, etc. Hope this information helps in your future product planning and development.", "create_at": 1620500200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product", "channel": "product_updates", "user": "maryjones", "message": "Thanks for sharing, Amanda. It's great to see that our performance packages are well received in the market. We'll definitely take this into account as we plan for the next range of enhancements.", "create_at": 1620500300000}}
